cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper is about image classification, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of sparse representation (cs.LG) and graph-based methods (cs.AI) for classification. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of Laplacian eigenmapping (cs.NE) and evaluates the performance on image databases (cs.MM).
